{"tid":1489692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］老母終於拋棄垃圾tvb 叫我幫手下戴其他apps","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T02:58:43.000Z","uid":198595,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c697fa2076766d3e317d25504c3cdc76743d36bc","tid":1489692,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"一路以黎我成日都同老母文宣<br />\n但我老母都算係幾怕事個啲人黎<br />\n又覺得又遊行個啲唔應該搞咁多<br />\n同埋睇左咁多年tvb都幾信tvb<br />\n個啲fake news佢有時真係會信<br />\n當然我地仔女同佢講返又會再懷疑下<br />\n<br />\n一見到就屌tvb放毒<br />\n終於佢拋棄tvb<br />\n比部手機我幫佢down下其他apps<br />\n之前都想過但個陣佢仲係好信tvb<br />\n哎好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係We connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n證明同屋企人長期文宣係有用（當然可能我老母一直唔係好藍）<br />\n<br />\n見到有啲手足同屋企人關係因為呢件事搞到唔係咁好<br />\n希望你地屋企人都有we connect既一天<br />\n不拋棄 不放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jKiXNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jKiXNW.jpg&h=5a709cba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fe16d22c621c487b2ffc62345c5ab6966ecc656","tid":1489692,"uid":141419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:37:21.000Z","msg":"屋企隻紅軍.....仲好深紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854904654805ca029add93cda47639a245438bb2","tid":1489692,"uid":198595,"like":1,